5: and repeats that until it gets some data in. 直到Arduino 收到電腦送來資料.
6: Then it waits for a byte in the serial port, and 當它由USB收到資料後, 它就會送出三個感應器的值給電腦
7: sends three sensor values whenever it gets a byte in.
